  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p>All tastefully decorated rooms have bath, shower, minibar, satellite TV (pay movies), telephone, trouser press, WiFi and hairdryer. A safe is available at the front desk. </p>
<ul>
<li>Standard Twin Room (A3) sleeping 2 people is as above</li>
<li>Standard Single Room (F1) has the facilities as above, and the room is on request</li>
<li>Twin Room (B2) sleeps 2 people in a renovated superior room, and also includes tea and coffee making facilities</li>
<li>Deluxe Twin Room (C3) sleeping 2-3 people in a harbour view room, seating area and twa and coffee making facilities</li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
